* Trivial pass-through models for purely mechanical connectors, used only
* so that `pcb sim` can generate a netlist for the whole board.
*
* J1 (XLR3) and J2 (3.5mm jack) contribute no electrical behavior of their
* own: in the testbench the phantom supply is injected directly on P2/P3
* and the capsule stimulus directly on MICIN, i.e. exactly where these
* connectors would otherwise hand off to the outside world. The models
* below are therefore empty subcircuits (no internal elements) - they
* exist purely to satisfy the "every component needs a SpiceModel" rule.

.SUBCKT CONN3 A B C
.ENDS CONN3
